{144}{MORP14}{You may keep your life.  Now, tell me what you know. }
{145}{}{我来自一个避难所，我愿意告诉主宰者位置。}
{146}{}{否则呢？}
{147}{}{我什么都不会告诉你。}
{148}{MORP15}{ No? Then I will take the information from you.  Guards! }
