{155}{MORP18}{ Give me the information or die a slow...lingering...death. }
{156}{}{你觉得杀了一个避难所居民，主宰者会高兴吗？}
{157}{}{我只跟主宰者说话。}
{158}{MORP19}{ Ahh...So you are the Vault dweller I've been hearing about.
