{159}{}{那我们就把你装进袋子里带走，怎么样？}
{160}{}{我也是。}
{161}{MORP20}{ A spy? Very foolish of you.  It will be
 difficult to report to him when you are dead, won't it? }
{162}{MORP21}{ You are
