{203}{}{其实，还有一些问题。}
{204}{}{不用了，谢谢。}
{205}{MORP36}{ Of course. Please.  Continue.}
{206}{MORP37}{ Yes, but you
 are...forgiven.  Go in peace, my child. }
{207}{MORP38}{ No, but with faith and
